snippet.textDisplay:
For all the people confused out there, Naat is a piece of POETRY (No matter with or without music) in praise of Prophet Muhammad  (S.a.w.w). And Qawwali is something which is a combination of poetry (in praise of ANY honorable personality) presented with some traditional Indian instruments.
So it can be called BOTH.
